1
00:01:09,560 --> 00:01:10,720
Come, dear.

2
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:16,800
Dear, do you want
to ask anything to him?

3
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:19,560
Once my parents are okay with him

4
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:21,640
then there is nothing to talk.

5
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:32,760
Why are you wearing this attire?

6
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:35,800
Where is the sari?
Where are the jewelleries?

7
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:38,320
You dreamt it again?
You don't have any other work?

8
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:41,240
If you marry and have children

9
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:43,880
then why will I dream of it.

10
00:01:45,240 --> 00:01:48,520
Will I get any chance in this life
of having a function in this house?

11
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:50,160
God knows.

12
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:52,040
You can think of that later.

13
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:53,840
First prepare my tiffin.

14
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:58,600
Good morning, Daddy. - Morning.

15
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:00,760
What's the news? - Same old thing.

16
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:02,440
Crime here and scam there. - Lunch.

17
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,640
Take it. - Nothing will change.

18
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:05,000
First think about
marrying your daughter

19
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:06,760
then you can think
about the whole world.

20
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:10,680
She started early in the morning.
- She didn't even stop.

21
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:12,280
She was even dreaming of it.

22
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:15,320
Bye, daddy. - Bye.

23
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,600
Just wave your hand
and send her to office.

24
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:19,920
Don't you think, you should
be sending her to in-laws house.

25
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:22,320
Yes, Mr. Sachin. Please wait.

26
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:24,080
I am leaving. I am on the way.

27
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:25,840
It's Sachin.

28
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:33,960
Bhumi. You go to the
supermarket lane, right?

29
00:02:34,040 --> 00:02:35,840
Yes. - Drop me there.

30
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:38,640
No, I won't drop you.
- Why? Even the car is empty.

31
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:41,520
This is not a share
auto to drop everybody

32
00:02:41,640 --> 00:02:43,000
when it's empty.

33
00:02:58,320 --> 00:02:59,720
Tada!

34
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,480
What's going on?

35
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:08,600
Photo session.

36
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,680
For followers.

37
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:12,720
#MondayMotivation

38
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,040
If they see you
early in the morning,

39
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,920
how will they get motivated?

40
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:18,120
Madam. - Not you,

41
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:21,400
those who invented the
front camera should be punished.

42
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:23,120
I can't punish him so,

43
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:25,080
from tomorrow I will ban
cell phones inside the office.

44
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:30,400
Hi, ma'am. I made a beautiful plan

45
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:32,360
for the factory/warehouse/office.

46
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:34,120
You will love it. Check it out.

47
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,240
It's so nice, right?

48
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,880
Yes, it is. - Thank you.

49
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,480
Use it for your house.

50
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:49,960
Sorry, ma'am.
- This is not your hostel

51
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:51,920
that you can come at anytime.
It's an office.

52
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:54,040
I am just 10 minutes late, ma'am.
- 10 minutes?

53
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:56,360
Leaving holidays,
your working days are 280.

54
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:57,800
If you are late for
10 minutes everyday,

55
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,800
then you are late for
2800 minutes for a year.

56
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:02,040
That means, it's nearly 47 hours.

57
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:05,040
If one working day is of 9 hours,
then it is roughly 5 days.

58
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:09,400
So, calculate your
pay minus 5 days loss.

59
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:17,560
Oh, God! Whoever marries her...

60
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:19,560
Yes, whoever marries me...

61
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:23,560
Did I say it out loud?
- Bring that phone here.

62
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,000
Bring it here.

63
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:30,520
I want this month's sales
report on my table by evening.

64
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:32,440
Ma'am. - Bring me the report

65
00:04:32,520 --> 00:04:33,680
and take your phone back.

66
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,760
Uncle! Good morning. Please come.

67
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:38,600
Hi, morning.
Sit, sit. - Please come in.

68
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:40,800
So, this is the project idea,
uncle. - Nice.

69
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:43,000
And this concept is pretty good.
- I really liked that too.

70
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:43,880
Yeah.

71
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:57,960
Why do you scare them so much?

72
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,640
They don't have
much responsibilities,

73
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:00,880
at least they should be afraid.

74
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:03,520
I am afraid that you will scold me,
forgetting that I am MD.

75
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,520
Not at all.

76
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,760
So, what's up?
What is your mom saying.

77
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:14,480
Same old thing.
She is going out to meet them

78
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,480
because I am scolding her
if she brings anyone at home.

79
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:20,480
Why don't you adjust
yourself because of her, then?

80
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:23,120
If I want to stay
together for lifetime,

81
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:24,400
first I should connect to him.

82
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:28,200
I hope you find your
connection very soon.

83
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:20,320
Hi. - Hi.

84
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:23,200
You told me to come urgently
from Paris. What's the matter?

85
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:25,000
I want to go to India.

86
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:27,760
Why do you want to go there?
- You know,

87
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:30,680
wherever you look, you just
see black coats and white beards.

88
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:35,320
Even if you come out, you
just see tall buildings and cars.

89
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:38,280
It's been so many days,

90
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:42,640
I am missing those trees,
fields and traditional attires.

91
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,040
Now, what do you say?

92
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:46,720
You were saying, there's
some project in India, right? - Yes.

93
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,440
Tell them,
we are ready to take the project.

94
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:50,280
I need a break from here.

95
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,800
You are thinking about taking break?

96
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:55,120
Hi, sir.
- Let me break some news to you.

97
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,160
Have a seat, sir.

98
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:58,640
Thank you.

99
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:01,560
When I saw you on the dais

100
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:04,640
you looked like upcoming
billionaire. When I see you here,

101
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:07,440
you look like a college student.

102
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:09,560
Okay, I will come to the point.

103
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,720
Sure, sir. - I will give you a deal

104
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:14,840
which will increase your
bank balance to 200 crores.

105
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:18,040
200 crores?

106
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,880
If you are okay, I will
make the papers ready by tomorrow.

107
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,080
Thank you.

108
00:07:21,440 --> 00:07:23,600
But no thanks, sir.
I am not interested.

109
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:27,240
Did you listen the numbers
correctly? It's 200 crores.

110
00:07:28,400 --> 00:07:30,320
After 2, there are nine zeroes.

111
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:32,480
I already told you,
I am not interested.

112
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:34,880
I thought, you only looked
like a college student.

113
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:36,600
Even your thinking is the same.

114
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:40,640
I know, money is very necessary.

115
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,120
But that is not the only
thing that is necessary.

116
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:43,720
Nice meeting you.

117
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:48,400
Hey, 200 crores?

118
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:51,600
I am just speechless
after telling that.

119
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:53,440
How can you reject that so simply.

120
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:55,800
You forget about that 200 crores

121
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:57,880
and get two tickets to India.

122
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:06,840
What Madam, didn't you
like the guy you met that day?

123
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,880
No.

124
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:11,920
The boy said okay
after seeing the photo

125
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:14,640
but my daughter said no
without even seeing the photo.

126
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:16,840
Leave it, Madam.
He was a bit average.

127
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,680
Was he? - Yes.

128
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:21,880
Just see this once.
- Shall I tell the truth?

129
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:24,480
That last guy was better.
- Shut up.

130
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:26,040
You will tell
something to everybody.

131
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:27,400
Shall I bring you coffee?

132
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,080
Go, bring it. - Okay.

133
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:31,480
If I won't purchase anything you
people will tell me not to sit here.

134
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:35,920
You are good looking
in person than the photo.

135
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:39,320
Whom are you searching?

136
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:42,800
Are you waiting for somebody?
- Where is your daughter?

137
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:45,880
She won't come.
- Oh, she won't like coffee?

138
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:48,440
She won't like the concept
of this kind of meetings.

139
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:53,120
Then, why did you call me?
- Talk to me, son.

140
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:55,840
If I like you,
then I will talk to her.

141
00:08:57,120 --> 00:09:00,440
I thought, meeting in the
coffee shop is like a new trend.

142
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:03,960
People will be open minded.
But, she is not even present here.

143
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:08,040
I can imagine,
how my future will be with her.

144
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:09,800
Son...

145
00:09:17,680 --> 00:09:19,920
Hi, Daddy. - Hey.

146
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:25,400
Why is this house so silent.
Where is Prabhavati?

147
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,520
She is not here.

148
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:29,240
She went to the temple.

149
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:32,000
Oh, she is not back yet? - No.

150
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:34,960
She went to circumambulate
700 times for your wedding.

151
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:37,120
She went to pray to God.

152
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:39,800
Hail Lord Venkatesh.
- I am not so sure.

153
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:42,400
Oh, she is already here.

154
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:43,600
Give me that phone. I will call her.

155
00:09:43,680 --> 00:09:45,360
Where will she go?
She will be back soon.

156
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:47,720
There she is.

157
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:57,440
Oh, God.

158
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,040
Oh!

159
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,920
You look tired.

160
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:04,920
Oh, God.

161
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:07,640
My legs are paining. - Oh, God.

162
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,880
I am tired.

163
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:12,840
Where did you go? - Can't you see.

164
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:16,520
I went to Venkateshwara temple.
Take the offering.

165
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:21,960
New sari,
offering, flowers, leg pains.

166
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:23,440
You are managing it all very nicely.

167
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:25,560
But, if someone goes to
temple they will crush the coconut

168
00:10:25,640 --> 00:10:27,240
not bring the coconut to the house.

169
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:32,280
Won't you change? - I won't change.

170
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:34,880
Mom, marriages won't
happen like this.

171
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:38,080
Then tell me, how marriages happen?
I will do it like that.

172
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:41,400
Just making me sit like a doll,

173
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:43,800
or scanning me if
I they like me or not.

174
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:45,080
I can't do those.

175
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,600
Who rejected you?

176
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:51,160
You are only rejecting them, saying
you are not connecting with them.

177
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:53,320
Should I connect with
whoever you show me?

178
00:10:53,400 --> 00:10:56,640
If you want to connect with
somebody, you should see him first.

179
00:10:57,600 --> 00:11:01,560
Women of your age are having
babies and sending them to school.

180
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:05,520
And here I am, searching
a husband for you like a mad woman.

181
00:11:05,880 --> 00:11:07,480
I am very unlucky.

182
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:09,240
I can't tolerate all this.

183
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:13,520
Will you say something...
- Sachin.

184
00:11:14,760 --> 00:11:15,880
Satyam.

185
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:17,480
Hello, Satyam.

186
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:20,480
Good morning, ma'am.

187
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:23,280
Ma'am, after thinking
deeply I made another design.

188
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:25,240
If you see this,
your mind will be blown. Trust me.

189
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:28,680
How much will you take?

190
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:30,760
Thank you.
I know, you will like this for sure.

191
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:32,440
Also, I am comfortable
for any negotiations between us.

192
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:34,600
Just give me whatever you like.
- Not for this design.

193
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:36,600
I asked as you had to do it again.

194
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:42,560
Thank you, ma'am. Sarla,
please think about your likes.

195
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:44,320
Please, don't say
anything about my sketch.

196
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:47,720
We are about to start
a new manufacturing unit.

197
00:11:48,160 --> 00:11:50,920
Once we start it, I will inform you.
You can visit that day.

198
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:54,280
Madam.

199
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,800
What are you seeing? - Madam.

200
00:11:56,880 --> 00:11:59,000
Give me the phone. Give me.

201
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:01,840
Here!

202
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:07,200
What is this?

203
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:09,640
I try to hide it inside, ma'am.

204
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:11,360
But, it comes out bursting.

205
00:12:11,800 --> 00:12:13,520
What is that? - Talent, ma'am.

206
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:15,920
Next time, if I see something
like this you will loose.

207
00:12:16,160 --> 00:12:17,720
What will I loose, ma'am?
- Your job.

208
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:20,720
Monster.

209
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:25,560
Why did you shout at that architect?

210
00:12:25,920 --> 00:12:29,400
Our company's concept and the
design he made is totally different.

211
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:31,000
He should've at least
used his common sense.

212
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:34,760
Correct,
but don't be too strict, Bhumi.

213
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:37,280
Even our office staff
is afraid of you.

214
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:40,560
No student likes
to go to school, uncle.

215
00:12:40,800 --> 00:12:42,360
Everybody just wants to play.

216
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:45,680
But, when they study
their future will be bright.

217
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:48,080
I am not talking about them.

218
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:52,040
You are being too
strict for yourself.

219
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:57,160
When I was not strict,
nobody took me serious.

220
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:59,400
Now, when I am being strict

221
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:02,120
nobody wants me to be with them.

222
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:06,880
If I tell you the truth

223
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:10,280
I don't even remember,
how I was back then.

224
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:13,520
I don't even know, how should I be.

225
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:49,000
Hello, Akash.
- Hello, Uncle, How are you?

226
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:50,080
I am good.

227
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:51,920
How was your travelling?

228
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:54,120
Gautam said, you are coming here.

229
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:56,120
If you are free tomorrow, I will
come and meet you in the office.

230
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:59,040
You are not some outsider.
Come home.

231
00:13:59,120 --> 00:14:00,120
Sure, uncle.

232
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:05,760
Do you know how he is?
- Yeah, I know.

233
00:14:06,160 --> 00:14:08,400
Hey, you said you wanted
to see sari and skirt.

234
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:09,640
Here, size of buildings
are increasing

235
00:14:09,760 --> 00:14:11,640
and size of clothes are decreasing.
- Stop it.

236
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:12,840
This is the problem with you.

237
00:14:12,920 --> 00:14:14,760
You don't see them and
you won't allow us to see.

238
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:26,480
Hi, uncle. - Hi, Akash.

239
00:14:28,880 --> 00:14:31,400
You reminded me of my son,
I am so happy that you came.

240
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:33,960
Do you remember him? Akash.

241
00:14:34,040 --> 00:14:35,880
Hi, aunty. - How are you, son.

242
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,520
Yes, I am good. - How is my son.

243
00:14:37,640 --> 00:14:38,760
He is fine, aunty.

244
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,400
Tell him to come and meet us

245
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:42,520
at least once a year.

246
00:14:43,680 --> 00:14:45,920
Okay, I'll bring you some coffee.
- Okay, aunty.

247
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:48,240
I saw your interview on CNN.

248
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:50,880
I felt very proud. - Thanks, uncle.

249
00:14:51,680 --> 00:14:53,480
You will leave early or
will you be here for some days?

250
00:14:53,560 --> 00:14:56,040
Actually,
I have some important work here.

251
00:14:56,160 --> 00:14:57,320
Okay. - Yes, uncle.

252
00:14:58,080 --> 00:14:59,320
Come Bhumi.

253
00:15:00,400 --> 00:15:01,760
