01:01:47,240 --> 01:01:49,240
Hey, you are here for? - Volunteers.

1022
01:01:49,320 --> 01:01:51,880
Hey, watch. Learn something
from them. - Okay, okay.

1023
01:01:51,960 --> 01:01:53,280
Write their names too. - Okay.

1024
01:02:09,960 --> 01:02:12,120
What? Swathi won't dance?

1025
01:02:12,200 --> 01:02:14,560
Rahul don't like dancing
her on the stage.

1026
01:02:14,640 --> 01:02:16,680
He don't want boys
teasing her from the crowd.

1027
01:02:16,760 --> 01:02:19,640
Who is he to control her?
- He is his boyfriend, so.

1028
01:02:19,720 --> 01:02:21,160
So, he won't respect his girlfriend?

1029
01:02:21,360 --> 01:02:23,200
If you are in his place,
you will do the same.

1030
01:02:23,280 --> 01:02:24,800
If I was in his place

1031
01:02:24,920 --> 01:02:26,600
and if my girlfriend
would like to dance

1032
01:02:26,800 --> 01:02:28,880
I would've enjoyed cheering
her from the crowd.

1033
01:02:29,680 --> 01:02:30,840
Okay, come.

1034
01:02:37,920 --> 01:02:41,360
Now what? If that dance is
cancelled, our program will be flop.

1035
01:02:41,440 --> 01:02:42,320
I will do it.

1036
01:02:45,120 --> 01:02:46,760
Are you sure? - Yeah.

1037
01:02:47,280 --> 01:02:49,000
I should go and practice. - Bye.

1038
01:02:49,200 --> 01:02:50,280
All the best.

1039
01:02:52,600 --> 01:02:55,560
Will she able to do it?
- Do we have any other option?

1040
01:02:56,040 --> 01:02:58,360
You danced very beautifully.

1041
01:02:58,440 --> 01:03:00,760
Hello, I was the best
dancer in my school.

1042
01:03:01,200 --> 01:03:02,120
Is it?

1043
01:03:02,520 --> 01:03:03,760
Then why didn't you say that first.

1044
01:03:04,120 --> 01:03:05,600
We were so tensed
till the last minute.

1045
01:03:05,680 --> 01:03:08,200
I didn't want to participate.

1046
01:03:08,280 --> 01:03:09,720
I did it for you.

1047
01:03:09,800 --> 01:03:12,920
I didn't want the
program to be flop.

1048
01:03:13,000 --> 01:03:13,880
Oh!

1049
01:03:14,120 --> 01:03:17,680
Anyway, I don't know whether
you heard the claps or not,

1050
01:03:17,760 --> 01:03:19,840
but I can still hear them.

1051
01:03:20,760 --> 01:03:24,760
'I felt like I was on cloud
nine when he was praising me.

1052
01:03:25,440 --> 01:03:29,560
'I felt like kissing
my mom because she forced me'

1053
01:03:29,640 --> 01:03:31,600
'to go to dance
school in childhood.'

1054
01:03:34,080 --> 01:03:35,840
Here, here.

1055
01:03:35,920 --> 01:03:37,400
Lift it. Lift it.

1056
01:03:37,520 --> 01:03:39,880
Hey. Throw it this side.
- Very good.

1057
01:03:39,960 --> 01:03:43,280
This way. Come on.
- Very good. That side.

1058
01:03:44,840 --> 01:03:46,840
Madam, dance was so nice.

1059
01:03:47,600 --> 01:03:49,120
Thank you. - What do you say guys?

1060
01:03:50,600 --> 01:03:53,600
If audience say once more,
artist will do it again, right?

1061
01:03:53,720 --> 01:03:57,000
Just do it once more for us.
Just one step.

1062
01:03:57,880 --> 01:04:02,520
We just get to see it once,
and practice and all only with him?

1063
01:04:03,480 --> 01:04:04,720
Let's go.

1064
01:04:09,360 --> 01:04:12,200
Madam, if you get bore with him,

1065
01:04:12,280 --> 01:04:14,040
my door is always open.

1066
01:04:23,280 --> 01:04:25,440
You are sad because you
lost the quiz competition?

1067
01:04:27,960 --> 01:04:28,840
Hey.

1068
01:04:29,640 --> 01:04:30,800
Cheer up, Bhumi.

1069
01:04:31,000 --> 01:04:32,400
It was just a small thing.

1070
01:04:33,000 --> 01:04:34,320
That was not a small thing.

1071
01:04:34,720 --> 01:04:36,400
I never failed in anything.

1072
01:04:36,640 --> 01:04:38,280
If you win always,
it won't be thrilling.

1073
01:04:38,400 --> 01:04:40,840
You must lose sometimes
to enjoy the thrill of the win.

1074
01:04:46,160 --> 01:04:47,080
Chocolate.

1075
01:04:48,920 --> 01:04:51,200
Thank you.
- You can say it by smiling.

1076
01:04:51,480 --> 01:04:53,760
Think that was the first
prize in the quiz competition.

1077
01:04:55,600 --> 01:04:56,520
Bhumi.

1078
01:04:57,760 --> 01:04:59,160
You look beautiful when you smile.

1079
01:05:04,880 --> 01:05:06,480
'You look beautiful when you smile.'

1080
01:05:21,120 --> 01:05:22,680
You are doing the
same thing from evening.

1081
01:05:22,760 --> 01:05:25,080
Stop seeing yourself in the mirror.

1082
01:05:27,120 --> 01:05:29,960
Many people said that
my smile is beautiful.

1083
01:05:30,720 --> 01:05:33,200
But I never felt
this special about it.

1084
01:05:37,320 --> 01:05:40,080
See, he gave me this chocolate.

1085
01:05:40,160 --> 01:05:42,080
Will you frame it or what?

1086
01:05:42,200 --> 01:05:45,560
He gave my favourite things.
I think, he likes me.

1087
01:05:45,840 --> 01:05:49,000
There is a big difference
between liking and recognising it.

1088
01:05:49,560 --> 01:05:52,560
You think he doesn't know,
but I think he does.

1089
01:05:53,560 --> 01:05:55,880
If you switch off the light,
I will go to sleep.

1090
01:06:21,240 --> 01:06:22,520
You guys here to beat me?

1091
01:06:25,520 --> 01:06:28,400
I don't think it is nice
to fight inside the college.

1092
01:06:28,680 --> 01:06:31,000
Bhumi.

1093
01:06:32,040 --> 01:06:33,200
Bhumi.

1094
01:06:33,400 --> 01:06:34,880
Why are so tensed? What happened?

1095
01:06:34,960 --> 01:06:36,720
In the ground,
Dhanush's gang and Akash...

1096
01:06:36,800 --> 01:06:39,320
Comment him again?
Our boy walked away calmly, right?

1097
01:06:39,600 --> 01:06:41,880
Back in the day,
Dhanush was talking rubbish

1098
01:06:41,960 --> 01:06:43,560
and Akash didn't even dare to fight
them. He didn't even looked angry.

1099
01:06:43,640 --> 01:06:45,360
Hello, first listen to me.

1100
01:07:33,680 --> 01:07:36,120
Did he beat them so bad?
- Not just a little...

1101
01:07:36,240 --> 01:07:37,920
...but very badly.

1102
01:07:38,320 --> 01:07:40,040
Why do you think he beat them?

1103
01:07:40,120 --> 01:07:43,000
I too don't know.

1104
01:07:43,080 --> 01:07:45,240
What are you thinking,
please tell me?

1105
01:07:45,320 --> 01:07:47,640
He beat them because Dhanush
was commenting on me, right?

1106
01:07:47,720 --> 01:07:49,480
It doesn't matter, what I think.

1107
01:07:49,560 --> 01:07:51,840
What he thinks matters.

1108
01:08:35,480 --> 01:08:37,160
What is this? - Shivaratri.

1109
01:08:37,600 --> 01:08:38,760
Do you know any temple nearby?

1110
01:08:38,840 --> 01:08:40,400
I have it in a cupboard in my room.

1111
01:08:42,640 --> 01:08:43,880
You are looking beautiful.

1112
01:08:44,440 --> 01:08:45,560
You are so beautiful in sari.

1113
01:08:46,600 --> 01:08:49,920
Cinema heroes and college
guys have the same reaction

1114
01:08:50,040 --> 01:08:52,520
when they see a girl in sari.

1115
01:08:52,600 --> 01:08:55,200
Nothing like that.
I saw many girls in sari

1116
01:08:55,320 --> 01:08:56,880
but I never told this to anyone.

1117
01:08:59,320 --> 01:09:00,920
Today is a holiday.
What are your plans?

1118
01:09:01,320 --> 01:09:02,440
Nothing.

1119
01:09:04,640 --> 01:09:07,080
My friends just went to the match.
- You are not going?

1120
01:09:07,160 --> 01:09:08,920
One second. Hello.

1121
01:09:12,120 --> 01:09:13,120
Yeah.

1122
01:09:13,640 --> 01:09:14,680
Okay.

1123
01:09:15,440 --> 01:09:16,720
Will you say it?

1124
01:09:17,600 --> 01:09:18,600
Okay.

1125
01:09:20,960 --> 01:09:22,080
Girlfriend?

1126
01:09:22,360 --> 01:09:23,480
Just like her.

1127
01:09:24,200 --> 01:09:25,240
Mother.

1128
01:09:26,640 --> 01:09:28,640
Seriously,
do you have any girlfriend?

1129
01:09:28,760 --> 01:09:30,560
No. - Sure?

1130
01:09:30,760 --> 01:09:32,280
Why are you asking that?

1131
01:09:32,480 --> 01:09:36,080
You look handsome, talk nicely.

1132
01:09:36,480 --> 01:09:38,240
Even you fight when it's necessary.

1133
01:09:38,480 --> 01:09:40,960
In simple words,
you look like a hero.

1134
01:09:41,440 --> 01:09:43,960
Oh, is it? Nobody else
felt it that way I guess.

1135
01:09:46,240 --> 01:09:48,040
Nobody is there in my heart.
It's true.

1136
01:10:03,520 --> 01:10:04,720
Hello, paper?

1137
01:10:04,800 --> 01:10:06,120
Sorry, sir. - Okay.

1138
01:10:06,400 --> 01:10:10,080
What if, Akash is also
confused to ask me out?

1139
01:10:10,480 --> 01:10:12,160
I will ask him whether
he likes me or not.

1140
01:10:12,240 --> 01:10:13,960
Don't think, just ask him.

1141
01:10:16,280 --> 01:10:19,080
Can girls take the first step?

1142
01:10:19,400 --> 01:10:21,040
Do you want to wait for few years?

1143
01:10:33,120 --> 01:10:35,000
Hey, are you able to
understand what am I saying?

1144
01:10:36,680 --> 01:10:38,400
Just think about your parents.

1145
01:10:38,680 --> 01:10:40,840
Remember, how many hopes
your parents must have on you.

1146
01:10:40,960 --> 01:10:42,920
You didn't study
all this for her, right?

1147
01:10:43,240 --> 01:10:44,680
You are a lucky fellow.

1148
01:10:45,680 --> 01:10:47,800
Don't feel bad,
because she rejected you.

1149
01:10:48,200 --> 01:10:49,320
Be happy.

1150
01:10:49,920 --> 01:10:51,400
If I was in your place,

1151
01:10:51,800 --> 01:10:53,040
I would've been so happy.

1152
01:10:53,640 --> 01:10:55,960
I would've partied all night
thinking my future didn't stop here.

1153
01:10:57,640 --> 01:10:59,680
You would've known if
you fall in love with someone.

1154
01:11:00,200 --> 01:11:03,760
Yes. I never loved anyone
nor I will love anyone.

1155
01:11:13,280 --> 01:11:15,640
What is there in this love.

1156
01:11:15,960 --> 01:11:18,840
Just giving flowers and talk
with each other the whole night.

1157
01:11:19,160 --> 01:11:21,280
You can get girlfriend
anytime in your life.

1158
01:11:21,640 --> 01:11:26,000
But think about your goal,
if you miss now, you can't reach it.

1159
01:11:26,680 --> 01:11:28,920
Whatever is lost,
we can get it later.

1160
01:11:29,000 --> 01:11:32,200
But if you waste your time,
it won't come back.

1161
01:11:34,520 --> 01:11:36,200
I never wasted time till now,

1162
01:11:36,600 --> 01:11:39,480
also I will never waste my time
in this useless things like love.

1163
01:11:47,600 --> 01:11:48,680
Bhumi.

1164
01:12:04,600 --> 01:12:05,480
You are leaving?

1165
01:12:06,080 --> 01:12:07,040
Yes.

1166
01:12:07,800 --> 01:12:09,360
Even I have a flight in the evening.

1167
01:12:09,960 --> 01:12:12,880
What else?
- Nothing. I came here to say, bye.

1168
01:12:13,200 --> 01:12:14,680
Yeah, yeah. Bye, Bhumi.

1169
01:12:15,000 --> 01:12:17,840
Don't know, when we will meet again.

1170
01:12:20,440 --> 01:12:22,400
Okay, be in touch.

1171
01:12:22,480 --> 01:12:23,360
Bye.

1172
01:12:34,440 --> 01:12:37,560
'I felt like he was
directly saying to me.'

1173
01:12:38,120 --> 01:12:40,720
'Whatever he said to him,
I felt it was just for me.'

1174
01:12:40,800 --> 01:12:43,840
'Few questions are answered
without even finding the answer.'

1175
01:12:44,200 --> 01:12:47,640
'Now I know,
what Akash has in his heart.'

1176
01:12:47,720 --> 01:12:50,680
'I felt happy before when
he said no one is in his heart.'

1177
01:12:50,840 --> 01:12:54,000
'But I understood that,
even I am not there in his heart.'

1178
01:12:55,400 --> 01:12:58,000
'If we read the
book again and again'

1179
01:12:58,080 --> 01:13:00,880
'will the story change in the end?'

1180
01:13:01,480 --> 01:13:05,920
'If you think it will change,
then you are a fool.'

1181
01:13:15,040 --> 01:13:17,400
What happened? Did you tell him?

1182
01:13:18,320 --> 01:13:19,320
What did he say?

1183
01:13:20,800 --> 01:13:21,960
Did he say yes?

1184
01:13:25,360 --> 01:13:26,520
No, mom.

1185
01:13:27,440 --> 01:13:29,680
He is not correct for me.
- What happened?

1186
01:13:30,280 --> 01:13:31,680
Didn't he like you?

1187
01:13:33,120 --> 01:13:34,520
Leave him.

1188
01:13:34,840 --> 01:13:39,960
Just say one word, I will bring more
handsome and nice guys then him.

1189
01:13:40,680 --> 01:13:42,040
Just leave it, mom.

1190
01:13:42,840 --> 01:13:45,400
This marriage and
all is not my thing.

1191
01:13:45,480 --> 01:13:46,520
What do you mean?

1192
01:13:46,960 --> 01:13:49,160
You won't marry?

1193
01:13:49,440 --> 01:13:51,680
I believed you and
I stopped praying.

1194
01:13:52,120 --> 01:13:56,240
So now, pray to get rid of me.

1195
01:13:56,520 --> 01:13:58,200
I am so unfortunate.

1196
01:13:59,480 --> 01:14:01,360
You are like a burden on my heart.

1197
01:14:01,440 --> 01:14:03,880
Prabha. What are you saying?

1198
01:14:04,200 --> 01:14:05,680
Go out of here.

1199
01:14:06,440 --> 01:14:07,720
Go.

1200
01:14:15,200 --> 01:14:16,600
Responsibilities are
same for mother and father

1201
01:14:16,680 --> 01:14:18,080
over their children.

1202
01:14:18,440 --> 01:14:20,120
But, in this house
it is not the same.

1203
01:14:20,840 --> 01:14:22,560
Here, nobody cares.

1204
01:14:33,280 --> 01:14:35,120
Even if you are not interested
in marrying your daughter,

1205
01:14:35,200 --> 01:14:37,240
at least did you think about it?

1206
01:14:41,960 --> 01:14:44,080
I am neither worries nor thoughts.

1207
01:14:44,160 --> 01:14:46,120
nor I take the responsibility,

1208
01:14:46,560 --> 01:14:47,600
okay?

1209
01:14:49,680 --> 01:14:54,320
Do we just make children
just to marry them, Prabha?

1210
01:14:54,600 --> 01:14:56,160
You are right.

1211
01:14:56,440 --> 01:14:58,960
Marriage is necessary, but that is
not the only thing that's important.

1212
01:15:01,400 --> 01:15:03,520
We have children with high hopes.

1213
01:15:04,080 --> 01:15:08,520
We work hard to raise them,
and educate them beyond our means.

1214
01:15:08,880 --> 01:15:10,200
And give them whatever they need.

1215
01:15:11,040 --> 01:15:13,960
Just to marry them with someone?

1216
01:15:14,680 --> 01:15:16,920
We do all this because
we want to see them live happily.

1217
01:15:17,760 --> 01:15:21,440
Why can't we wait,
till they search for themselves?

1218
01:15:22,480 --> 01:15:24,920
Why can't we know
their choices, Prabha?

1219
01:15:27,600 --> 01:15:29,600
Why can't we give the
same amount of time to a girl

1220
01:15:29,720 --> 01:15:31,560
like we give to a boy.

1221
01:15:32,160 --> 01:15:34,800
Why do we hurry only
for girls marriages?

1222
01:15:36,640 --> 01:15:39,520
If we ask them,
people say, what will society think.

1223
01:15:40,200 --> 01:15:42,960
If we marry her in some
place where she is not happy

1224
01:15:43,760 --> 01:15:45,560
who will suffer in the end?

1225
01:15:50,320 --> 01:15:53,280
When a girl turns 13,
you should sanction her.

1226
01:15:54,280 --> 01:15:57,240
If she turns 25, just marry her
with someone and loose the burden.

1227
01:15:57,320 --> 01:16:00,720
I can't think like
an outmoded father.

1228
01:16:02,080 --> 01:16:03,640
In my eyes,

1229
01:16:03,840 --> 01:16:07,640
I am not a failure,
if I don't do her marriage.

1230
01:16:08,200 --> 01:16:10,760
I can't make her marry
where she doesn't want to marry.

1231
01:16:15,200 --> 01:16:17,600
Not until, if there's
a situation where I am ashamed

1232
01:16:17,720 --> 01:16:19,600
let anybody think
whatever they want.

1233
01:16:20,800 --> 01:16:23,320
I really don't care and I mean it.

1234
01:17:02,600 --> 01:17:05,040
Morning, Daddy. - Hey, morning.

1235
01:17:05,960 --> 01:17:09,120
Daddy, I am going to Alak
for one week for Bindu's marriage.

1236
01:17:09,200 --> 01:17:10,440
We are organising it.

1237
01:17:10,640 --> 01:17:12,840
Good, good. Enjoy.

1238
01:17:13,040 --> 01:17:16,400
She is helping in everybody's
marriage, but she won't do it.

1239
01:17:17,360 --> 01:17:19,800
We can argue and can
even change the judgement

1240
01:17:20,920 --> 01:17:23,160
but we can't change
your mother's heart.

1241
01:17:23,240 --> 01:17:24,600
It's really impossible.

1242
01:17:32,040 --> 01:17:34,520
Mom, I am leaving in the evening.

1243
01:17:34,800 --> 01:17:36,400
If I say no, will you stop?

1244
01:17:36,680 --> 01:17:38,240
You never listen to me.

1245
01:17:39,840 --> 01:17:41,040
Now, what?

1246
01:17:41,240 --> 01:17:43,320
I should get married, right?

1247
01:17:43,960 --> 01:17:48,080
Mom, who can think that
I should be good more than you.

1248
01:17:49,200 --> 01:17:50,840
You see, whoever you like.

1249
01:17:51,160 --> 01:17:53,000
Huh, really?

1250
01:17:57,440 --> 01:17:58,640
Yes.

1251
01:18:00,800 --> 01:18:03,200
Just see,
how nice guy I will search for you.

1252
01:18:03,680 --> 01:18:06,960
I will kill the guy who rejects you.

1253
01:18:48,560 --> 01:18:50,760
What is that look?
Give me that phone.

1254
01:18:51,840 --> 01:18:52,720
Give me.

1255
01:18:56,840 --> 01:18:58,960
Why are you guys so serious? Laugh.

1256
01:19:03,560 --> 01:19:04,560
What happened to you, ma'am?

1257
01:19:04,640 --> 01:19:07,280
You changed your
dressing and your style.

1258
01:19:07,440 --> 01:19:09,160
What is the fun
being the same person

1259
01:19:09,280 --> 01:19:10,600
in the marriage and in office?

1260
01:19:10,720 --> 01:19:13,640
There should be some entertainment
in one's life, right?

1261
01:19:14,840 --> 01:19:17,160
You are giving us
some shocking news.

1262
01:19:18,480 --> 01:19:20,600
This look suits
you very much, ma'am.

1263
01:19:21,240 --> 01:19:23,920
Yes, ma'am. Looks like your
age has been decreased five years.

1264
01:19:24,040 --> 01:19:27,400
So, is it fine if I have
still five years left to marry?

1265
01:19:30,960 --> 01:19:32,800
Look, they all are here.
- Hey, Bhumi.

1266
01:19:32,880 --> 01:19:34,160
Uncle.

1267
01:19:35,480 --> 01:19:36,880
All your friends came?

1268
01:19:36,960 --> 01:19:39,240
If you have any problem, just ask.

1269
01:19:39,320 --> 01:19:40,360
