01:37:51,800 --> 01:37:54,160
you are breaking up,
and you are leaving.

1522
01:37:54,760 --> 01:37:56,040
Then who will think about me?

1523
01:37:57,440 --> 01:37:59,000
Only you have feelings?

1524
01:37:59,920 --> 01:38:01,080
I don't have it or what?

1525
01:38:02,600 --> 01:38:04,400
Do you know, why I came
here after all these years?

1526
01:38:05,840 --> 01:38:07,720
Why am I roaming around you?

1527
01:38:08,240 --> 01:38:09,720
Did you think about it even once?

1528
01:38:11,120 --> 01:38:13,000
I didn't come here for any project,

1529
01:38:13,280 --> 01:38:14,640
or any marriage function.

1530
01:38:17,040 --> 01:38:18,760
I came here only for you.

1531
01:38:31,000 --> 01:38:32,800
When I knew that you loved me,

1532
01:38:33,680 --> 01:38:35,800
I couldn't stay there and
I searched for you and came here.

1533
01:38:43,640 --> 01:38:46,080
Hi, how are you?
Yes, I have reached.

1534
01:38:46,600 --> 01:38:47,680
I am so sorry.

1535
01:38:50,280 --> 01:38:51,400
Akash.

1536
01:38:51,880 --> 01:38:53,680
Anjali. What are you doing here?

1537
01:38:54,000 --> 01:38:56,640
How is your friend, Bhumi?

1538
01:38:56,720 --> 01:39:00,200
After college, we didn't meet. - Oh!

1539
01:39:00,720 --> 01:39:04,120
She didn't tell
you but she loved you.

1540
01:39:06,360 --> 01:39:08,480
She just used to think about you.

1541
01:39:11,480 --> 01:39:14,080
She always tried to talk to you.

1542
01:39:15,520 --> 01:39:17,760
At that moment

1543
01:39:18,240 --> 01:39:21,040
I saw it from your view.

1544
01:39:28,320 --> 01:39:31,560
I didn't want to participate.
I did for you.

1545
01:39:33,400 --> 01:39:35,400
Seriously,
you don't have any girlfriend?

1546
01:39:35,480 --> 01:39:36,680
No.

1547
01:39:46,920 --> 01:39:48,320
After knowing that,

1548
01:39:48,600 --> 01:39:50,360
I didn't like what I was doing?

1549
01:39:51,000 --> 01:39:52,440
I didn't know where to find you.

1550
01:39:52,760 --> 01:39:54,280
I didn't know what were you doing?

1551
01:39:55,320 --> 01:39:58,320
I searched for you.
I called everybody whoever I knew.

1552
01:39:59,920 --> 01:40:01,640
I searched you in social media.

1553
01:40:02,360 --> 01:40:03,640
You were nowhere.

1554
01:40:04,600 --> 01:40:07,280
Where are you?
You are still in love with me?

1555
01:40:07,920 --> 01:40:09,800
Or did you forget me?

1556
01:40:10,840 --> 01:40:12,400
Gautam. - Yes.

1557
01:40:12,480 --> 01:40:15,560
She is in Hyderabad.
She is running a startup company.

1558
01:40:17,520 --> 01:40:20,600
Guess what?
My father is funding the company.

1559
01:40:22,720 --> 01:40:26,240
Hey, Akash. One more thing.
She is not married yet.

1560
01:40:26,600 --> 01:40:27,880
I don't know why,

1561
01:40:27,960 --> 01:40:30,000
after hearing that,
I couldn't control my happiness.

1562
01:40:30,240 --> 01:40:33,640
I couldn't stay there any longer.

1563
01:40:35,440 --> 01:40:38,600
I thought you will
be excited when you see me.

1564
01:40:39,480 --> 01:40:41,320
But, when I saw you
behaving so casually

1565
01:40:41,800 --> 01:40:43,720
I didn't know how to react.

1566
01:40:46,960 --> 01:40:48,560
I thought you moved on.

1567
01:40:49,640 --> 01:40:51,560
I wanted to observe
you very closely,

1568
01:40:51,840 --> 01:40:53,400
so I took up this project.

1569
01:40:54,000 --> 01:40:55,840
I felt very attractive

1570
01:40:55,920 --> 01:40:59,760
when I saw you changed totally.

1571
01:41:01,240 --> 01:41:05,200
So, I loved you,
when you made me recognise myself.

1572
01:41:06,760 --> 01:41:08,880
I just wanted to know

1573
01:41:09,320 --> 01:41:11,320
what you think about me,
so I lied about the bridesmaids.

1574
01:41:12,440 --> 01:41:14,280
I listened that you loved me.

1575
01:41:14,640 --> 01:41:17,480
But that was first time I saw,
how you felt about me.

1576
01:41:18,160 --> 01:41:19,880
I didn't know your love.

1577
01:41:20,640 --> 01:41:22,280
I made you feel very sad.

1578
01:41:22,920 --> 01:41:24,680
You left that night,

1579
01:41:25,920 --> 01:41:27,320
I thought you were angry on me.

1580
01:41:28,120 --> 01:41:31,520
I was waiting that
you will come back.

1581
01:41:33,000 --> 01:41:34,200
But,

1582
01:41:36,760 --> 01:41:38,920
you are leaving this watch...

1583
01:41:40,960 --> 01:41:42,480
now I can understand,

1584
01:41:43,200 --> 01:41:46,600
you left me on that day itself.

1585
01:41:51,160 --> 01:41:53,720
I thought I understood
your love very late,

1586
01:41:56,000 --> 01:41:57,800
but now I get that,

1587
01:42:00,800 --> 01:42:02,520
it is very late.

1588
01:42:19,080 --> 01:42:22,160
This is a small project.
- I am saying I'll do it.

1589
01:42:22,760 --> 01:42:23,920
I need to talk to you.

1590
01:42:24,000 --> 01:42:26,400
Akash, please.
I don't want to talk to you.

1591
01:42:35,680 --> 01:42:38,120
Sister, everyone is leaving.

1592
01:42:46,960 --> 01:42:48,920
Call Akash.

1593
01:42:53,520 --> 01:42:54,920
Mom is waiting, uncle.

1594
01:42:55,520 --> 01:42:56,560
I need to go.

1595
01:43:00,960 --> 01:43:03,440
Sarla, bring the bag.

1596
01:43:30,440 --> 01:43:32,800
You already came? Come here.

1597
01:43:36,080 --> 01:43:37,280
Let's go.

1598
01:43:40,440 --> 01:43:43,200
Bhumi. They will
arrive anytime soon.

1599
01:43:43,280 --> 01:43:44,440
Get ready.

1600
01:44:10,480 --> 01:44:11,880
Go Bhumi.

1601
01:44:21,400 --> 01:44:24,440
Please smile, Madam.
You look beautiful when you smile.

1602
01:44:32,040 --> 01:44:34,680
Did you connect at first sight?

1603
01:45:12,200 --> 01:45:14,960
If you love someone, let them know.

1604
01:45:15,160 --> 01:45:17,360
You should know,
what he thinks about it.

1605
01:45:17,600 --> 01:45:19,160
You didn't even question

1606
01:45:19,280 --> 01:45:22,280
and you are waiting for an answer.
How will you know?

1607
01:45:25,760 --> 01:45:29,360
Go. Already you guys
waited for so long.

1608
01:45:48,480 --> 01:45:50,600
What is all this, Prabha?

1609
01:46:06,760 --> 01:46:10,960
Hello, aunty.
- Son. The girl you love...

1610
01:46:11,880 --> 01:46:13,120
Is her name Bhumi?

1611
01:46:16,480 --> 01:46:17,560
Yes, aunty.

1612
01:46:17,640 --> 01:46:20,080
Did you guys study
in the same college?

1613
01:46:21,760 --> 01:46:23,040
How do you know?

1614
01:46:41,000 --> 01:46:45,160
Her love is very pure.
That made Akash come here.

1615
01:46:45,560 --> 01:46:47,800
I just helped them be together.

1616
01:46:48,640 --> 01:46:51,160
At last, you daughter is
marrying and you are sending her.

1617
01:46:51,360 --> 01:46:53,720
I am not sending
her after the marriage.

1618
01:46:53,960 --> 01:46:56,320
She must need someone to guide her.

1619
01:46:59,000 --> 01:47:02,160
You gave me the watch and you left?
You decided you wanted to leave me.

1620
01:47:02,240 --> 01:47:03,600
No chance.

1621
01:47:05,960 --> 01:47:07,440
However you cut me.

1622
01:47:07,520 --> 01:47:10,000
I was about to go
and meet your parents.

1623
01:47:11,240 --> 01:47:13,320
In the mean time aunty
called me and asked about us.

1624
01:47:13,440 --> 01:47:15,760
So, now we are here after that.

1625
01:47:16,160 --> 01:47:19,000
When you came here,
why didn't you meet me directly?

1626
01:47:19,080 --> 01:47:20,320
Why do you think your client

1627
01:47:20,400 --> 01:47:22,680
kept the meeting in
the hotel where I stay?

1628
01:47:22,800 --> 01:47:24,320
She told she will be coming
but she was not there. Why?

1629
01:47:24,480 --> 01:47:26,440
So, that was all your plan?

1630
01:47:26,920 --> 01:47:29,120
You look innocent but you are not.

1631
01:47:29,240 --> 01:47:30,520
What can I do?

1632
01:47:30,960 --> 01:47:34,640
I couldn't see your love.
I had to put up an act for that.

1633
01:47:36,600 --> 01:47:38,760
You waited for me this long.

1634
01:47:39,240 --> 01:47:41,040
I should at least fight this, right?

1635
01:47:41,120 --> 01:47:43,760
Hello, I didn't wait for you.

1636
01:47:43,840 --> 01:47:45,760
Just, I didn't connect to anybody.

1637
01:47:47,480 --> 01:47:48,640
Why are you laughing?

1638
01:47:48,720 --> 01:47:50,560
You didn't have this ego in college.

1639
01:47:51,240 --> 01:47:52,800
You made me like this.

1640
01:47:55,000 --> 01:47:57,880
You didn't even say it yet. - What?

1641
01:47:58,480 --> 01:48:00,840
That you like me. - Wait for that.

1642
01:48:01,760 --> 01:48:03,120
How long?

1643
01:48:03,280 --> 01:48:05,360
Till that 'Bhumi' (sky)
meets the 'Akash' (land).

1644
01:48:06,040 --> 01:48:09,520
I will tell your mom,
she will do it easily.
